{"tid":1993751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲: 香港人停止街頭抗爭, 就可以搞死泛民","createTime":"2020-04-29T03:56:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T06:04:08.000Z","uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"36a447b68aa0c3ee2c6d065c030fad8b2d35d94f","tid":1993751,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10158128527192225/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F589657224%2Fposts%2F10158128527192225%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=C0QxMr2ftqWfBh1dRblImLc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=86ce900e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/589657224/posts/10158128527192225/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：疫情未過，送頭又來。送頭日程表出現啦，五一勞動節大遊行，泛民鳩戴口罩，幫政府搞出來的防疫措施，那些限制聚集令，更加方便衙差捉人和控告入罪。街頭示威位位罰款二千元，政府拉人又搞到創收。<br />\n<br />\n選舉是要叉電的，護法運動、中大陣地戰、理工堡壘大血戰的電，已經在區議會選舉用完，電兔區議員可以用幾年。<br />\n<br />\n九月是立法會選舉，要做新的電源。<br />\n<br />\n泛民在這個時候搞送頭日程表，是招惹共產黨對付他們，但如果很多素人出去、很多港獨、城邦出去，共產黨又只能對付素人和一大堆不是泛民的前線行動者，跟住泛民高叫血債票償，又一次靠憤恨投票當選。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>故此，見到日程表，不出去就可以搞死泛民</strong>，泛民要出自己人。Game是這樣玩，不玩就是玩，我在毛澤東政論班講的辯證法。學習這個，不需要很高智力，但需要謙卑。"},{"pid":"1a4e8a0081e07dad9e849085bfaefa8e545a0241","tid":1993751,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔只搞死泛民<br />\n連香港都搞死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/28/jRKlfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F28%2FjRKlfh.png&h=0d24661e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f16f843e57b25b3d71ad3cf5e0a1cdea5c701495","tid":1993751,"uid":22068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a4e8a0081e07dad9e849085bfaefa8e545a0241","tid":1993751,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"唔只搞死泛民<br />\n連香港都搞死埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/04/28/jRKlfh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F04%2F28%2FjRKlfh.png&h=0d24661e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:59:22.000Z","msg":"想問一句：一方面搞五一黃金周，另一方面行動攬炒，係精神分裂定點？"},{"pid":"cad68c7d5dd8b5d3c619153de2cc1042b0ccd84f","tid":1993751,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T03:59:49.000Z","msg":"唔想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8062090de5173e64d767a0f0788d45502fa8c18","tid":1993751,"uid":2889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"條撚樣真係得高登仔先會捧佢"},{"pid":"406b809bd18a6ee8041c16464efcf6afb2f1a12f","tid":1993751,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c8062090de5173e64d767a0f0788d45502fa8c18","tid":1993751,"uid":2889,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:10:14.000Z","msg":"條撚樣真係得高登仔先會捧佢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:11:34.000Z","msg":"依家既高登仔已經係全部青山派班甩皮甩骨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74a64b3c8331aaca26ea48c8fd5ceed4d38f6df8","tid":1993751,"uid":306614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:11:52.000Z","msg":"泛民幾時搞過日程表? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edae8c315946a9c0fcad0fea9d0d307fcab0674f","tid":1993751,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:12:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0fdb69cab7b926d2195f5fbb7926f0950474086","tid":1993751,"uid":186431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"建議睇精神科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86e44897bc4d3a9777d16421dc6cb873b8fe8c16","tid":199